{"tid":2047348,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"東亞傳洽售中港銀行業務","createTime":"2020-06-02T04:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T06:03:31.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4413673922029ddd1f1a1eff07587ac20489eebc","tid":2047348,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》引述知情人士報道，東亞銀行(00023)正初步磋商出售本港和內地的銀行業務。<br />\n<br />\n美國對沖基金Elliott Management持有東亞約8%股權。據報，Elliott批評東亞近年管理欠佳，出售一項或兩項銀行業務，可視為該基金的勝利。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，東亞3月已委託高盛對銀行資產進行策略性審查。該行旗下一家保險子公司，也計劃放售；而本港與內地的銀行業務可以分開出售，此取決於兩地監管機構的審查。出售資產事宜仍在評估中，與潛在投資者的討論尚處於初步階段。"},{"pid":"4ce03457c6ba39c21d393134b57f94051caccf90","tid":2047348,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"可能賣畀四蝗行之一既農行？"},{"pid":"b30a9069f5158849027c8280581a763dc8de6ae5","tid":2047348,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"別讓xxx跑了系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516b8781af929f1a9ed1d775b59be9012b9e2a41","tid":2047348,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:03:12.000Z","msg":"即刻拎錢走人唔玩?"},{"pid":"bfcc81a7994aa6e37e9d5142d35aa374701b10bd","tid":2047348,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2efe237ebb13700079ad3b031eb7398412a5cf","tid":2047348,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"516b8781af929f1a9ed1d775b59be9012b9e2a41","tid":2047348,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:03:12.000Z","msg":"即刻拎錢走人唔玩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"所有嘢都係「傳」je<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80cd405f7bcb79c2eec57e0a9128738df64b151","tid":2047348,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep